Tracy died from multiple gunshot wounds.

TvT project: WBALTV News 03.08.2012

Priscila's body was found with gunshot wounds on the BR-232 highway.

> Homophobia made yet another fatal victim in Pernambuco. This time they were a [trans woman], in the municipality of Sairé, in the state's Agreste.
> 
> The victim's body was found this Friday morning (6), on the BR 232 highway, near the Monte Castelo condominium in the municipality. The murdered [trans woman] was brown in color and had red hair, as well as a sun tattoo on her back. 
> 
> After being taken to the IML in Caruaru, it was found that the cause of death was six shots from a firearm, which hit the victim's arms, back and neck. She has not yet been identified.

Karla's body was found at the 70 kilometre point on the Nandaime-Rivas highway. She was naked and her body showed signs of strangulation.

Reportedly Karla lived in Jinotepe and used to offer sexual services on the south highway between kilometer points 66 and 80 and her body had been thrown from a van at dawn.

>
> Dilşeker's throat was cut and this killed her. Dilkeşer's funeral, Muratpaşa district of the district of the Forensic Medicine Institute after the examination was sent to the house in the neighborhood.
>
> Antalya Police Department, took a look at the camera images around the house. Dilşeker's ex-boyfriend and close friends also applied to the testimony of the Antalya Police Department is conducting a large-scale investigation.
>
> Last month, a group of people in the Altindag neighborhood of Antalya organized an action against trans people on the grounds that trans people were sex workers in the neighborhood. Activists who claimed that they could not go out with their families after the darkening, said they would keep watches with sticks in their hands.

column8: Calz Ignacio Zaragoza, Santa Martha Acatitla, Iztapalapa
column15:
The victim was attacked in her apartment by her partner and a friend, who, after stabbing her, abandonded the body on an avenue.

TvT partner organisation Centro de Apoyo a las Identidades Trans: NoticiasTerra.com    22.09.2012

According to the police, the victim was sleeping as four men entered her apartment in the early morning, who shot her. Da Silva was taken to hospital, where she died.

The murder took place on Av. Laiá Paiva in Mandacaru.

TvT project: Portal Correio, online portal, 23.07.2012

Neighbours heard the detonation but did not report anything. The victim’s body showed a gunshot wound in the head and was fettered.

TvT partner organisation Centro de Apoyo a las Identidades Trans: NoticiasTerra.com.mx   24.07.2012

The victim was killed together with three other people. The suspect belongs to a local gang and "has admitted that he has committed all the murders in the name of honour killing".

TvT project: Dunya News TV 27.07.2012

The victim, who was from an indigenous Guiana community, lived in an illegalised situation and did sex work.

The murder took place on Av. dos Bandeirantes.

TvT project: Roraima Hoje, online portal, 29.07.2012

Patsy was shot twice in the chest at the corner of Doctor Miguel Silva and Francisco I. Madero streets by Fidel Lombera Barragán, an architect and former deputy for the PRD.

Barragán was arrested.

Patsy's murder was not recorded on the official TDoR 2012 list released by Transgender Europe (TGEU).

https://menosdiasaqui.blogspot.com/2012/07/

Pâmela was shot and killed at the entrance of a nightclub as she was talking to two men. Her two companions were injured, but both survived.

After her murder STVBrasil issued the following statement:

> We who make STVBrasil - Sociedade Terra Viva express our grief at the murder of the friend and [trans woman] Pâmela Scheyfon, barbarously murdered, in the early hours of Monday, 30, leaving a nightclub in the city of São José de Mipibu - RN.
> 
> Pamela, who had been elected Queen of Diversity in the latest edition of the Gay Parade of the Wild, was young, a good person with life, and dear to everyone in the community.
> 
> The crime, still unexplained, occurred when Pamela was talking to two men at the door of a nightclub, and the three of them were surprised by another man who appeared and began firing gunfire, mortally hitting Pamela and injuring the other two men. After the crime the killer escaped on foot and the police have no information about his identity.
> 
> STVBrasil - Sociedade Terra Viva, through its legal advice, will be providing support to the family members of Pâmela and will follow the case.
>
> To family and friends our solidarity.

The body of the victim was found on a vacant lot at the Contorno Highway on the night of Tuesday 31st July.

The crime happened next to a fuel station in the municipality of Serra. According to information from the Civil Police, a pipe possibly used for the consumption of crack was found next to the victim.

She wore a pink sweater, red bra and earrings.
